Puppet module: profile

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages profile software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include profile              # Install and run profile with standard configurations.
include profile::disable     # Disable profile service.
include profile::disableboot # Disable profile service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include profile::absent      # Remove profile package.

DEPENDENCIES:
